{
  "stem": "4830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they have a standing order not to allow any Jew to survive if they evacuate any place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said that for that opportunity, if he cannot order them away, then we can defend the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we worked out a very good plan that he had his study where he accepted everybody who came to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his desk was reinforced by steel blades on the top and on the side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he placed us in strategic position all over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He studied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The door was always left open in this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said that if he cannot convince them to leave, then he will light a cigarette, at which point we should start to shoot at them and defend the house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because otherwise, everybody will get killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we agreed to this task.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And fortunately, they really came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were around 15 fascist soldiers, very well-equipped, who came to execute the Jews in the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he managed to tell them that they cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There are brothers in here-- wounded brothers-- whom they care for, and they cannot kill their own brothers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they will get killed if we don't take care of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they should go to the front and fight the Russian rather than, you know, spend bullets on valueless Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he convinced them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He didn't light the cigarette, so we didn't have that confrontation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But we had one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this is the only one in which I participated a military style of confrontation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One of us was captured.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Somebody must have recognized him because we had excellent papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was captured by the fascists and was taken to the Fifth District headquarter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And our commander felt that if he's tortured he might tell where we are and who we are.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
